blueprint.description: Modular hex cell for train network. Build any stations you want from the inputs. Made for trains of 3 or less cars (1 engine, 1 or 2 cars). RHD. The station that's there is for personal transport using two engines facing opposite ways. The gates are connected to the signals in spots with green lights. If light is green you can cross, if yellow you can but you're rolling the dice, if red better wait.
blueprint.label: Hex cell blueprint
